{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, the SDN's central management mechanism helps optimize traffic flow and lessens congestion in the 5G network because of the massive volume of data traffic present there, which might cause congestion if improperly handled.",
    "In addition, SDN is used in the 5G networking system to manage resources and control traffic, as was already mentioned.",
    "SDN is therefore used to intelligently regulate the system's overall energy usage 53.",
    "In summary, SDN plays a significant role in the 5G ecosystem, such as dynamic network management, centralized control, network slicing, flexibility and agility, service orchestration, efficient resource Utilization, and reduced operational costs.",
    "The IoT devices learn to process the acquired data utilizing IoMT models."
  ]
}